{"tid":281343,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[無圖]撩耳屎好爽 ！！","createTime":"2017-06-12T15:39:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-13T12:11:20.000Z","uid":13590,"like":24,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"062050f32bfc67a302998a9560c09563a12a4ce5","tid":281343,"uid":13590,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T15:39:30.000Z","msg":"繼上次撩完耳仔後<br />\n耳仔痛左成個月<br />\n一用耳挖伸入去點到舊耳屎就痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n琴日用左枝藥水一滴<br />\n今日就輕鬆撩左舊黑色耳屎出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但係撩左出黎聽野唔覺得特別清<br />\n唔知係咪撩壞左隻耳仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/12/233759_0e4282adfcf0b9ae50ceaf7e5de6aad5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F12%2F233759_0e4282adfcf0b9ae50ceaf7e5de6aad5.jpg&h=af838a67&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5ccc514e96833a8834775ff775fa6d0838b49ac3","tid":281343,"uid":29863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T15:40:52.000Z","msg":"炭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"837d820e8704a6283a8fde2ec0c4577c89104eca","tid":281343,"uid":51250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T15:41:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8628fa9c73d86a2c3be97f4250141b6c255c7f29","tid":281343,"uid":97100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T15:41:20.000Z","msg":"屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />點做到"},{"pid":"ab2565b9db3d53a94a51d82a4063d28c3408eae6","tid":281343,"uid":62650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T15:42:51.000Z","msg":"乜藥水，介紹一下"},{"pid":"eef418b3cc310fb9b1448ab7b3fc70c0d0be5447","tid":281343,"uid":65128,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T15:43:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"51496601437d611c1311b620e12223764c0dcdd0","tid":281343,"uid":13590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T15:43:33.000Z","msg":"我細個個時耳仔已經成日塞住 特別係游完水之後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  但一直無去撩 <br />\n都係上個月先第一次用耳挖撩耳屎出黎 <br />\n唔知係咪上個月撩到耳仔流血所以變成呢舊黑色耳屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab1dc8a11974f52f43c8c394afbfa1a9b0863de2","tid":281343,"uid":16250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T15:43:58.000Z","msg":"咩味?"},{"pid":"ca819b1b9313e97ef8fd65d3bffe13c36941eb42","tid":281343,"uid":13590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T15:44:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>乜藥水，介紹一下</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n正美耳蘇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  香港品牌 藥房35蚊有支"},{"pid":"0e4b53e85774754bd98d289148775dce94340c8c","tid":281343,"uid":13590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T15:44:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咩味?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n因為滴左藥水所以係藥水味<br />\n但無滴就係惡臭味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都唔知仲可以點形容"},{"pid":"3d23a961e954603e1155f55882afff0bb81076e9","tid":281343,"uid":36417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T15:48:35.000Z","msg":"唔肯定有冇大舊野可唔可以滴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n定係搵醫生好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a16046b9ac7427af29c9f5b09279e233393aedd1","tid":281343,"uid":13590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T15:51:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔肯定有冇大舊野可唔可以滴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n定係搵醫生好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n用耳挖細力同慢慢挖下 如果挖到咁上下有野頂住左都唔方好野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n本來都準備定搵醫生算 但竟然用藥水一日搞掂左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3124abfc38809735d949da60e10b99b9e10d648f","tid":281343,"uid":66769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T15:51:22.000Z","msg":"有無試下味？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83f89f00fa97a221631362edd0a1342d28919d13","tid":281343,"uid":78046,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T15:52:08.000Z","msg":"點解要放係MacBook 上面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8be9e89f724bf45b1fa7b6f4c0cd2b5b79b55c24","tid":281343,"uid":13590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T15:52:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有無試下味？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無 震撼到想留低成舊原汁原味咁欣賞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1c2a78422f376da93351f8f1316dfa95f0f9326","tid":281343,"uid":78046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T15:52:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解要放係<span style=\"color: red;\">laptop</span> 上面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"a84d514e70a50f6f2b57f6d86dd6b894b6d5fb99","tid":281343,"uid":13590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T15:53:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解要放係MacBook 上面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係macbook黎<br />\n只不過我一路用電腦一路挖 <br />\n挖完放低係電腦好順手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d1070d919c100d21645210d75aec5449b48159f","tid":281343,"uid":108090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T15:56:02.000Z","msg":"可想而知<br />\n你平手打飛機都係射係部電腦上面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ebc94cf41f05855e05ea2f86019693cda7df442","tid":281343,"uid":13590,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T16:00:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>可想而知<br />\n你平手打飛機都係射係部電腦上面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我係藍絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4a77e407b8ee4d7f9698712cac4fe0390776838","tid":281343,"uid":36490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T16:06:32.000Z","msg":"咩藥水"},{"pid":"0662c2108ed3586a07682017f5f190cd538cf467","tid":281343,"uid":4210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T16:07:03.000Z","msg":"我油耳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68b825a99fade48869b7aa36d77f2189953ef625","tid":281343,"uid":36490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T16:07:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咩藥水</blockquote><br />\n自膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6af9d6190a7dada12e65cd55021f36906fe2a7ea","tid":281343,"uid":13590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T16:07:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咩藥水</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n上面答左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2d55762b10084e9ae380043f79b5f42b4a9b125","tid":281343,"uid":68558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T16:07:40.000Z","msg":"點先可以挖到咁大舊屎出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n平時挖都淨係挖到啲碎出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd82b468b3d7aafa6c201cb239f883560e193bbd","tid":281343,"uid":13590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T16:09:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我油耳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實我唔太識分我係咩耳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我嘅耳屎通常好重耳油味 同埋都幾硬下 睇圖就知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05af610aaf49145ad900d011e7c842851f0e4169","tid":281343,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T16:09:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>咩藥水</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n上面答左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n星期六沖去買返支先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c7b9a4fb6b2361b4cc06f9e5590eeed25373909","tid":281343,"uid":13590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T16:11:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點先可以挖到咁大舊屎出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n平時挖都淨係挖到啲碎出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔一定個個都有咁大舊耳屎嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我平時用手指撩都係得碎<br />\n用耳挖先撩到咁大舊"},{"pid":"0de0987456029177c91bc6f564f807ecc249de36","tid":281343,"uid":90123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T16:11:29.000Z","msg":"哇屌你成個耳塞咁"},{"pid":"8b6272da8aa0c3deb56c8b3f6f2002c815f2d46c","tid":281343,"uid":13590,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T16:12:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>哇屌你成個耳塞咁</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n拎左個耳塞出黎都唔太覺聽力好左其實先係我最擔心嘅野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"024074991ea3f7dbb94382504e6b971e5b4190b5","tid":281343,"uid":108090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T16:13:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>可想而知<br />\n你平手打飛機都係射係部電腦上面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我係藍絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nPMED<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85083d5519efa387cd7fe4cdbcebacb99e642f6c","tid":281343,"uid":28475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T16:13:34.000Z","msg":"之前耳膜前小小發炎<br />\n耳仔塞咗<br />\n一撩撩到舊係我耳窿成倍既耳屎<br />\n撩完通曬<br />\n通到有回音同埋暈暈地"},{"pid":"7f88438def74133fc0555b4c2a3885b8c6b66e79","tid":281343,"uid":113165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T16:14:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>哇屌你成個耳塞咁</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n拎左個耳塞出黎都唔太覺聽力好左其實先係我最擔心嘅野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n姐係你耳入面仲有好多耳屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb7dc27d51e275d8499754fdbd8d30120d5b4c1f","tid":281343,"uid":2869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T16:15:21.000Z","msg":"屌你成粒提子乾咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6c30970240608092957e98f5ab797eb646b69df","tid":281343,"uid":13590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T16:15:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>之前耳膜前小小發炎<br />\n耳仔塞咗<br />\n一撩撩到舊係我耳窿成倍既耳屎<br />\n撩完通曬<br />\n通到有回音同埋暈暈地</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有冇話咩原因會發炎？<br />\n我耳仔成日都有啲「搭搭」聲 好似耳鳴咁<br />\n宜家撩完都仲有都唔知咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb7430fe3f19759c37f823cfcd8a2c3a4946e6ab","tid":281343,"uid":13590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T16:16:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>哇屌你成個耳塞咁</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n拎左個耳塞出黎都唔太覺聽力好左其實先係我最擔心嘅野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n姐係你耳入面仲有好多耳屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我再撩到好入都無野啦喎 <br />\n舊耳屎又好完整咁撩出黎<br />\n唔好嚇我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"023329f6bcfd372350d8a07f0092c412cfbbc916","tid":281343,"uid":13590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T16:18:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌你成粒提子乾咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n大粒過提子乾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2a652c060740cbbd3b79b1f50089fe399949829","tid":281343,"uid":28475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T16:18:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>之前耳膜前小小發炎<br />\n耳仔塞咗<br />\n一撩撩到舊係我耳窿成倍既耳屎<br />\n撩完通曬<br />\n通到有回音同埋暈暈地</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有冇話咩原因會發炎？<br />\n我耳仔成日都有啲「搭搭」聲 好似耳鳴咁<br />\n宜家撩完都仲有都唔知咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我睇耳鼻喉科專科700蚊一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢會用部機幫你吸屎<br />\n小小痛但好撚爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲比支藥水同藥你"},{"pid":"3665105dfa19077182ccae6a50169b54d169920e","tid":281343,"uid":13590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T16:20:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>之前耳膜前小小發炎<br />\n耳仔塞咗<br />\n一撩撩到舊係我耳窿成倍既耳屎<br />\n撩完通曬<br />\n通到有回音同埋暈暈地</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有冇話咩原因會發