<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2a1396566e8994c3451803fa0e2c5f7471d60b5","tid":281343,"uid":1531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T17:19:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢d係患過中耳炎先會有<br />\n正常人唔會積到咁大舊耳屎"},{"pid":"e514c14f718aab6f40fc4439f1bcbf60dbb572be","tid":281343,"uid":3822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T17:21:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我係油耳好少會草到一大舊<br />\n通常都係痴哂落個邊<br />\n用耳挖挖出嚟又係一堆油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n聽落好似仲核突咁喎 <br />\n咁咪撩極都撩唔完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n都撩得完嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但feel到仲係成個耳窿都油淋淋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b61d56dc7d26cba341c6969d5201be26601bd94","tid":281343,"uid":13590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T17:32:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢d係患過中耳炎先會有<br />\n正常人唔會積到咁大舊耳屎</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n之前耳塞同耳嗚我都無太理佢<br />\n因為反正都無痛嘅情況出現（除非我自己搞粒耳屎）<br />\n所以無為意過有呢啲病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  要睇醫生了"},{"pid":"bf1f2489a6ef0d6c2eabe417bad3ef21e28df87d","tid":281343,"uid":19214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T17:39:17.000Z","msg":"其實唔係話人耳會自動排耳屎既咩？<br />\n到底點先會塞到咁"},{"pid":"98ec8ec72eaaba0d2781ebcb5b9d6bab515b9f0e","tid":281343,"uid":13590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T17:43:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實唔係話人耳會自動排耳屎既咩？<br />\n到底點先會塞到咁</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都想知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  會唔會係天生？"},{"pid":"c630f2470c152b7329b762e59a06813469ae38a7","tid":281343,"uid":71567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T17:48:46.000Z","msg":"我之前都有咁大舊！一樣樣！好爽<br />\n細個有過中耳炎 真係關事？<br />\n前幾年覺得唔係好聽到野 去睇醫生 佢幫我洗耳 仲話未見過有咁多耳屎嘅人 洗耳突發覺得聽野清咗好多<br />\n每次飛機降落 對耳都會痛到想喊 非一般嘅痛 加上耳嗚一日 唔知關唔關中耳炎事"},{"pid":"6625e12c84627168b6f15c657b18a55c2bdc1bc6","tid":281343,"uid":1531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T17:50:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實唔係話人耳會自動排耳屎既咩？<br />\n到底點先會塞到咁</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都想知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  會唔會係天生？</blockquote><br />\n我都有過<br />\n<br />\n細個耳道損過發埋炎<br />\n<br />\n後尾一時時會有耳塞<br />\n<br />\n終於前幾年無啦啦挖到出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢舊應該唔係耳屎 純粹係耳道發炎分泌物"},{"pid":"6aced887140eb3a64af4b7afdd42b5c5ae0091d3","tid":281343,"uid":51507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T18:00:36.000Z","msg":"記得好似個個人都有呢D大耳屎 但無害唔洗理人佢 唔好亂挖 好似有保護作用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7eecc3f744571c80cd694b61843b010f5415fb8d","tid":281343,"uid":122068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T18:08:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實唔係話人耳會自動排耳屎既咩？<br />\n到底點先會塞到咁</blockquote><br />\n好似係因為有啲人天生係唔識自動排耳垢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65e9f5c1aff628f910e6e848ea49c977181e75c5","tid":281343,"uid":119810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T18:11:12.000Z","msg":"屌 平時啲耳屎唔係啡黃色架咩"},{"pid":"0d80f7b3947c020690c74791194d57f7f0c69f25","tid":281343,"uid":119810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T18:11:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實唔係話人耳會自動排耳屎既咩？<br />\n到底點先會塞到咁</blockquote><br />\n好似係因為有啲人天生係唔識自動排耳垢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係咪因為太大舊"},{"pid":"058c503d0260a6d47ee9f1913a141f5f63d93e74","tid":281343,"uid":122068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T18:11:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔肯定有冇大舊野可唔可以滴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n定係搵醫生好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n細個開始游完水之後左耳仔成日塞 去到中學都係頂唔順睇醫生 先後開咗二次??油畀我的滴耳仔 希望可以軟化耳垢等佢自然排出但係冇用 跟住之後醫生才用水沖都係冇用. 最後去咗耳鼻喉科搞 冇見過舊耳垢 不過醫生一拎出嚟 聽到旁邊嘅實習醫生嘩咗好多聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f85b49efe5da4c7163185ac50a10074ecd73ebe2","tid":281343,"uid":13590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T18:33:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我之前都有咁大舊！一樣樣！好爽<br />\n細個有過中耳炎 真係關事？<br />\n前幾年覺得唔係好聽到野 去睇醫生 佢幫我洗耳 仲話未見過有咁多耳屎嘅人 洗耳突發覺得聽野清咗好多<br />\n每次飛機降落 對耳都會痛到想喊 非一般嘅痛 加上耳嗚一日 唔知關唔關中耳炎事</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我塔飛機又無好痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}